[[PageOutline]]
= Claypool Api IoC (Inversion of Control) =
----

== Exceptions ==
Claypool tries to help regulate erros by providing a simple way to extend and identify errors regardless of their position in the hierarchy (like python or java etc).

=== !ContainerError ===
!ContainerError can occur when searching the Application Context, in particular if some context contributor throws and unexpected error.
{{{
try{ 
    throw new Claypool.IoC.ContainerError(); 
}catch(e){ 
   if(e.name.match("Claypool.IoC.ContainerError")){ 
       //This will be true 
   } 
   if(e.name.match("Claypool.Error")){ 
       //This will be true 
   } 
} 
}}}
----

